The information contained in our health related applications are for educational purposes only and is not a substitute for medical and fitness advice from a doctor, Fitness experts and health care providers. Consult a health care provider for advice about any course of treatment or medical condition. Seek advice from Fitness Experts and Nutrition experts for Exercise and Diet activities.
